text: Ángela Indira Evans (born 21 July 1993) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a forward for Irish Women's National League club Kilkenny United WFC and the Panama women's national team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Pan American Games competitors for Panama Category:Footballers at the 2019 Pan American Games
